item.title: About
item.description: Hello everyone! I am SenlinOS. Use GNU/Linux to make comics. My Projects: SLOS-GIMPainter (Brush package for GIMP): GitHub. Do Not Update MyPaintBrushes-GIMP (Brushes): GitHub. (No need to update) Simplified Chinese Translation for AzPainter 2.x: No longer maintained. Homepage: SenlinOS.com Mirror Site: senlinos.github.io | senlinos.bitbucket.io Expand to view SenlinOS.com QRcode Desktop OS: Trisquel GNU/Linux、 Laptop OS: Xubuntu Software: AzPainter-V3 (Digital Line art)、GIMP-2.
